CatDescriptText: David Leo Lawrence was mayor of Pittsburgh from 1946 to 1958, and governor of Pennsylvania from 1959 to 1963.  He died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Two men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence seated at desk handing document to young man, and young woman in striped dress, gathered in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
